OL,3,CCampaigners call on Chancellor to ring
OL,4,Cfence childcare funding in budget
OL,6,FCampaigners have called on the
OL,7,FChancellor to ring fence funding for
OL,8,Fchildcare in next week's budget.
OL,10,FThey've been seeking more help for
OL,11,Fstruggling parents due to the ever
OL,12,Frising cost.
OL,14,FRecent figures show the average cost
OL,15,Fper child before any help is applied
OL,16,Fis #562 per month.
OL,18,FBut campaigners believe that figure
OL,19,Fdoesn't give a true picture.
