OL,3,CCampaigners call on Chancellor to ring
OL,4,Cfence childcare funding in budget
OL,6,FAnd this is why - very few people are
OL,7,Fusing full time childcare 5 days a
OL,8,Fweek.
OL,10,FThe bulk are using a few days a week
OL,11,Fbecause they can't afford any more -
OL,12,Fso that average figure would likely
OL,13,Frise if more people were using full-
OL,14,Ftime daycare.
OL,16,FCasey McGivern, Melted Parents NI told
OL,17,FUTV "a lot of working families in key
OL,18,Fservices like nurses, doctors,
OL,19,Fdentists are really struggling under
OL,20,Fthe crushing cost."
