OL,3,CCampaigners call on Chancellor to ring
OL,4,Cfence childcare funding in budget
OL,6,F"We hear all the time about people
OL,7,Fleaving work but one of the key
OL,8,Fdecisions people are taking is to cut
OL,9,Fhours."
OL,11,F"So there is a slow exit from work and
OL,12,Fthe more the costs increase, the more
OL,13,Fpeople withdraw."
OL,15,FThere is help out there - the
OL,16,Fgovernment at Westminster runs a tax
OL,17,Ffree childcare scheme giving 20
OL,18,Fpercent of bills - capped at #2k per
OL,19,Fchild.
