OL,3,CCampaigners call on Chancellor to ring
OL,4,Cfence childcare funding in budget
OL,6,FStormont has recently introduced a
OL,7,FChildcare Subsidy Scheme, giving a
OL,8,Ffurther 15% reduction - capped at #184
OL,9,Fper month - so far saving parents over
OL,10,F#8 million.
OL,12,FMany parents believe that the scheme
OL,13,Fhas already been cancelled due to
OL,14,Fprice rises.
OL,16,FHowever, in England there is also a
OL,17,Fscheme where parents get 30 hours free
OL,18,Fchildcare.
