OL,3,CCampaigners call on Chancellor to ring
OL,4,Cfence childcare funding in budget
OL,6,FThe cost of delivering childcare from
OL,7,FWestminster is significant - #1.8
OL,8,Fbillion extra allocated at last years
OL,9,Fbudget.
OL,11,FThe way Northern Ireland's budget
OL,12,Fworks is we get our fair share of that
OL,13,Ffunding - a Barnett consequential.
OL,15,FStormont can spend that money on
OL,16,Fwhatever it wants; it's not limited to
OL,17,Fchildcare - campaigners want that
OL,18,Fchanged.
