OL,3,CCampaigners call on Chancellor to ring
OL,4,Cfence childcare funding in budget
OL,6,FCasey McGivern told UTV "we have long
OL,7,Freceived equivalent funds in our
OL,8,FBarnett consequentials from childcare."
OL,10,F"We estimated in the financial year 23/
OL,11,F24 #154 million in equivalent funds
OL,12,Fsent to NI and #25 million was spent."
OL,14,F"The reason is because it isn't ring
OL,15,Ffenced, if we want to resolve the
OL,16,Fissue the Chancellor could make a bold
OL,17,Fdecision and ring fence our funds."
